<p><img src="https://cdn3.brettterpstra.com/uploads/2025/12/apex-header-2-rb.7518.jpg" width="800" height="226" style="margin:0 auto;clear:both;" class="header" /></p>
<p>I&rsquo;ve been busy improving <a href="https://brettterpstra.com//projects/apex">Apex</a> with some great new features and fixes. CSV tables, aria labels, and more.</p>

<p>Here are the highlights from the latest release.</p>

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#better-accessibility-with-aria-support" id="markdown-toc-better-accessibility-with-aria-support">Better Accessibility with ARIA Support</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#improved-plugin-installation" id="markdown-toc-improved-plugin-installation">Improved Plugin Installation</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#homebrew-installation-made-easy" id="markdown-toc-homebrew-installation-made-easy">Homebrew Installation Made Easy</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#script-injection-and-css-embedding" id="markdown-toc-script-injection-and-css-embedding">Script Injection and CSS Embedding</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#multi-file-document-modes" id="markdown-toc-multi-file-document-modes">Multi-file Document Modes</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#table-improvements" id="markdown-toc-table-improvements">Table Improvements</a>    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#table-header-columns" id="markdown-toc-table-header-columns">Table header columns</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#inline-csvtsv-tables" id="markdown-toc-inline-csvtsv-tables">Inline CSV/TSV Tables</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
