  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#inline-csvtsv-tables-1" id="markdown-toc-inline-csvtsv-tables-1">Inline CSV/TSV Tables</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#mode-dependent-features" id="markdown-toc-mode-dependent-features">Mode-Dependent Features</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#and-much-more" id="markdown-toc-and-much-more">And Much More</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://brettterpstra.com#get-the-latest-version" id="markdown-toc-get-the-latest-version">Get the Latest Version</a></li>
